### Phase 6: Timing Verification

- [ ] Timing tests run on target hardware (not simulator)
- [ ] Stress test with all tasks active simultaneously
- [ ] ISR storm test (maximum interrupt rate sustained for > 1 minute)
- [ ] Long-duration test (> 24 hours) to catch drift and accumulation
- [ ] Timing margin documented for each task (WCET vs. deadline)

